[{"id":"VR102520","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><include href=\"../Passage/VR102504.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">After boiling the flowers, the instructions say to</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR102520_rubric","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<div class=\"stimulus_reference\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"><p class=\"introduction passage-intro\">Read this set of instructions.</p><div class=\"passage\" xml:lang=\"ja\"><div class=\"prose prose_type:instructions style:1\"><div class=\"title\"><p class=\"title_line passage-title\">自宅でかんたん草木染め</p></div><p class=\"passage_para\">今日は春におすすめのタンポポを使った「<span class=\"ruby\"><span class=\"rb\">草木染</span> <span class=\"rt\">くさきぞ</span></span>め」をご紹介。意外にかんたんですよ。</p><p class=\"passage_para\">用意する物：</p><p class=\"passage_para\">タンポポの花</p><p class=\"passage_para\">シルクの<span class=\"ruby\"><span class=\"rb\">布</span> <span class=\"rt\">ぬの</span></span></p><p class=\"passage_para\">なべ</p><p class=\"passage_para\">ミョウバン</p><p class=\"passage_para\">ゴムの手ぶくろ</p><p class=\"passage_para\">染め方：</p><ol class=\"ordered_list style:2\"><li class=\"list_paragraph\">大きななべにいっぱいの水を入れて火にかける。<span class=\"ruby\"><span class=\"rb\">沸騰</span> <span class=\"rt\">ふっとう</span></span>したら、タンポポの花を入れて15分<span class=\"ruby\"><span class=\"rb\">煮</span> <span class=\"rt\">に</span></span>る。</li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">火にかけたまま、タンポポの花を取り出す。</li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">残った<span class=\"ruby\"><span class=\"rb\">液</span> <span class=\"rt\">えき</span></span>の中に布を入れ、中火で１時間ほど煮る。</li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">火を止めて、そのまま一晩置く。</li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">次の日、布を軽く洗う。３％のミョウバン液を作り、その液の中で４０分から１時間煮る。</li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">煮た布を２、３回洗ってかわかす。きれいな黄色に染まりますよ。</li></ol><p class=\"passage_para\">注意：</p><p class=\"passage_para\">染める液は手につくと、なかなか取れません。必ずゴムの手ぶくろを使いましょう。</p></div></div></div>"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">turn off the stove</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">take the flowers out</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">add more flowers</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">drain the water</p>"],"answer":1}]